@startuml
actor "Quản lý / Admin" as Reviewer
participant "Browser (approvals.html)" as Frontend
participant "RequestController" as APIController
participant "RequestService" as Service
database "Database" as DB

Reviewer -> Frontend : Nhấn Duyệt hoặc Từ chối
Frontend -> APIController : PUT /api/requests/{id}/review/employee/{reviewerId} (JSON: ReviewRequestRequest)
APIController -> Service : reviewRequest(id, reviewerId, req)
Service -> DB : Cập nhật Request status & reviewerId
DB --> Service : OK (Entity)
Service --> APIController : Trả về RequestDTO
APIController --> Frontend : HTTP 200 OK
Frontend -> Reviewer : Hiển thị "Đã cập nhật trạng thái đơn"
Frontend -> Frontend : Tải lại danh sách
@enduml
